HL983: If you want to learn a language as quickly as possible, nothing is faster than having a 1-on-1 teacher. A teacher can give you the personal attention you need to improve your language skills.

HL986: With online learning, you can learn from home, or anywhere with an internet connection. No more need to waste time traveling on the road. You can also learn at a time when it is convenient for you.
